Synapse::Monitor::Listener
==========================

Synapse::Monitor::Listener is a configurable tool which decides what to do when
certain predefined checks switch from one state to another.

See POD for details.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

   synapse-monitor-listener-cli --create-configdir
   synapse-monitor-listener-service install
   synapse-monitor-listener-service start

DEPENDENCIES

none

